en.elixir_lesson3_ex2_slide1_content:
Structs can be updated like maps.

```elixir
user = %User{name: "Alice", age: 25}
updated = %{user | age: 26}
# %User{name: "Alice", age: 26}

# Map.put also works
updated2 = Map.put(user, :age, 27)
```

